DT20061108221204.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n遊戲名稱：A3之帝國的興起<br />\n原文名稱：A3 Part.IV<br />\n類　　型：角色扮演<br />\n語言版本：繁體中文<br />\n設計公司：(國外) Actoz<br />\n發行公司：(台灣) 華義國際數位娛樂股份有限公司<br />\n公測日期：2006年5月25日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2NB69ux7l6w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2NB69ux7l6w&d=gd88IM%2FH5PesiZkjWSBWufM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=be28e439\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2NB69ux7l6w</a><br />\n<br />\n&lt;&lt;A3&gt;&gt; 係一隻標榜18+既韓國成人MMORPG, 亦係當時少有既 Semi-3D既 game (當時95% mmorpg係2D, 得天堂2 同 RO 係3D / 半3D). 隻game 好血腥, 會打到D怪爆升甩頭, 同埋d怪係大波露點既, 就連女主解法師芙蕾亞都有係宣傳MV或poster露點.<br />\n<br />\n隻game有兩個職 1. 法師 2. 戰士, 怪物都係d 巨人, 半人半蟲, 巨蟲 等等, 又係幾好玩既, 當個覺得佢畫面勁靚!<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲玩過上述遊戲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdfc32a341a8b819c3104ad423a0c24483473b6","tid":705908,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:57:03.000Z","msg":"A3搵唔到遊戲資料？"},{"pid":"7a1e48f655ed6aeadf0e28d7d8639e8bdaaf1783","tid":705908,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fdfc32a341a8b819c3104ad423a0c24483473b6","tid":705908,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T14:57:03.000Z","msg":"A3搵唔到遊戲資料？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"google or youtube &quot;A3 online&quot;"},{"pid":"827999f8565368474afbaeac3365c8ba9e8e0dde","tid":705908,"uid":12662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T15:51:37.000Z","msg":"A3 點會冷門呀"},{"pid":"1529e263badf61edf93bf0be8fc018ec191d7a2d","tid":705908,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"A3<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://acg.gamer.com.tw/acgDetail.php?s=5688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Facg.gamer.com.tw%2FacgDetail.php%3Fs%3D5688&d=gd88IM%2FH5PesiZkjWSBWufM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=8be8d5a6\" t